  "output_text": "The process begins when an employee submits a vacation request. Once the request is submitted, it is sent to the immediate supervisor for approval. The immediate supervisor receives the request and then registers the requirement.\n\nAfter registering the requirement, a decision point is reached. At this point, there are two possible paths the process can take. \n\nIn the first path, the system returns the application to the employee. This path leads directly to the end of the process.\n\nIn the second path, a notification is generated for the HR representative. The HR representative then completes the procedure. After the HR representative finishes their task, the process reaches the same decision point as the first path.\n\nRegardless of which path is taken, the process concludes at the end point."
